Explore metrics about achievements such as skills, levels and badges. To earn points please navigate to `Project -> Metrics -> Achievements`.

There are two ways that you can drill-down from the project metrics page to the project **achievement** metrics - by clicking the navigation icon on the top right:

![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)

**OR** by drilling down into the Achievements cards on the bottom of this page:

![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)
Achievement metrics display number of users that achieved each levels as well as offer a comprehensive achievements browser. The achievement browser allows project admins to locate skill, badges and level user achievements by utilizing powerful filters and displaying them in a tabular page-able and sort-able result set.
